sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant D as Django View
    participant V as VoyageAI
    participant M as MongoDB Atlas

    U->>D: Sends Query "Space dogs"
    
    par Vector Path
        D->>V: Embed("Space dogs")
        V-->>D: Vector [0.1, 0.5, ...]
        D->>M: $vectorSearch(Vector)
        M-->>D: [Doc A (Score 0.9), Doc B (Score 0.8)]
    and Keyword Path
        D->>M: $search("Space dogs")
        M-->>D: [Doc C (Score 5.0), Doc A (Score 2.0)]
    end

    D->>D: Calculate RRF Scores
    Note right of D: Doc A is in both -> High Score<br/>Doc B/C are unique -> Lower Score
    
    D->>U: Return Sorted List [Doc A, Doc C, Doc B]
